HEADWORD: chairperson
<hw>chairperson</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the officer who presides at the
meetings of an organization; -- same as <altname>chair{3}</altname> or
<altname>chairman{1}</altname>, but used to achieve a sex-neutral
register.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> president, chairman, chairwoman, chair.</syn>⟦br⟧
